He shewed it away and it headed west down the road.
He tried to follow it in his truck but lost track of it.
When he got back to the house it was by the back door eating out of the dog dish.
He shewed it away again and it ran behind the house between the animal pens and the barn.
He checked the dog dish and it was empty.
He was not sure if there had been food in it or not.
